Package: fdai
Title: FDAi - AI-Powered FDA Device Recalls Dashboard
Version: 2.0.0
Description: A Shiny web application that queries the openFDA API for medical
    device recalls, displays interactive visualizations, and generates
    AI-powered executive reports via OpenAI.
